      "date": "2012-12-05 18:31:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b64e6f08-3f06-11e2-856e-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
